Everything in spec/ is licensed under MIT, including:

  - ABI.md (specification document)
  - gen_bios_stub.py (clean-room BIOS stub generator)
  - gba_bios_stub.bin, gba_bios_stub.h (generator output)

The BIOS stub is a clean-room reimplementation of a small set of GBA SWI
entry points, written from public SWI contracts (GBATEK and similar).
It is NOT a dump or disassembly of Nintendo's GBA BIOS. See LEGAL.md §1
for the full provenance statement.

gbatek.htm is an external reference vendored for convenience; it is
third-party documentation (copyright Martin Korth) and is not covered
by this MIT grant. It is redistributed with attribution per the terms
on the upstream document. See ../NOTICE.

